body:
There’s this guy in my class who hates Captain Marvel

All week I’ve been hearing him say “she’s a trash character.” I haven’t spoken up. I’ve only abided my time for the right moment to strike. Today that came. I was in class with him and changed my iPad name to Rocco(a good friend of his)(also annoying). Then I went to airdrop and sent an image to the guys sitting around Mr. Trash. They showed it to him, all saying how it was from his friend. He got super upset. I won’t be there when he confronts Rocco, but god I wish I could be.

summary:
Alright I’m probably going to get a lot of hate for saying this but... Captain Marvel isn’t that great. 
She was the first SOLO...
body:
Alright I’m probably going to get a lot of hate for saying this but… Captain Marvel isn’t that great.

She was the first SOLO female hero but she was 100% not the first hero in the MCU.

Captain Marvel is extremely cocky and full of herself and the movie was definitely not living up to every other movie in phase 3.

She’s really overrated and overplayed by media just because of the female lead.

*Edit: I apologize if this post offended you everyone has their own opinions on things and this is just mine *

@captainmarvels @marvelmemesworld @avengersuniverse @captainmarvelsource @
